Package org.apache.tamaya.spisupport.propertysource

Class MapPropertySource

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.tamaya.spisupport.propertysource.BasePropertySource
      • org.apache.tamaya.spisupport.propertysource.MapPropertySource
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PropertySource
    public class MapPropertySource
extends BasePropertySource
    Simple PropertySource implementation that just takes a Map and an (optional) priority. Optionally the entries passed can be mapped to a different rootContext.
